Who am I ?

Trịnh Thái Anh is a lovely web developer / designer located in our lovely Earth. He has been working on it professionally for over 2 years. And still loves every minute of it.

That's enough of talking about myself in the third person. I love to enhance my friends's pictures since I was a child and this hobby has led me into the graphic-maniac field. At first I intended to be an animator and planned to follow that hobby in university fully motivated to become just that. One thing lead to another and 2 years later I found myself especially interested into the accessible website ever since I come to know about HTML (especially W3C web standard) in highschool, and I was a fully fledged web developer without ever planning to become one. Nowadays, I spend most of my free time in researching web development technologies with a high passion to become one of the awesome people to bring knowledge to everyone around the world through their small screens.

Projects

  • Capstone Project

    My graduate thesis defense project, a network monitoring system to track realtime status and collect network devices's datas. We worked on Scrum model with Web languages (PHP & HTML/CSS/Javascript) and deployed to CentOS

  • Interconnected tax system

    A simplified system of tax and land-related administrative procedures, included Category Management (users, depatments, administrative units as districts, wards, streets...) using MVC model with Web languages (ASP.NET & HTML/CSS/Javascript) and deployed to Windows

  • Online public service level 3

    A service to ensure the full provision of information about the process and procedures, file, duration, service fees, and allow users to fill in and send forms online to agencies or organizations providing services. Built using MVC model with Web languages (ASP.NET & HTML/CSS/Javascript) and deployed to Windows

  • Company website

    Promote the latest news, software, services of company to the public. At the same time allow users to contact directly in real time with the staff of company. Built using MVC model with Web languages (ASP.NET & HTML/CSS/Javascript) and deployed to Windows

  • Management and Resettlement System

    A system of planning, management and resettlement of households in Ho Chi Minh city, included Category Management (districts, wards, streets...). Built using MVC model with Web languages (ASP.NET & HTML/CSS/Javascript) and deployed to Windows

  • Land Information System

    Develop a system for managing land-related changes in land procedures based on available company land data, included Category Management (users, depatments, administrative units as districts, wards, streets...). Built using MVC model and MongoDB combine with Web languages and deployed to Windows
